video_title: What’s Next for AI Agents? - SuperAI Singapore 2025
description:
Learn more about SuperAI: superai.com
Follow us on X: x.com/superai_conf

Panel: What’s Next for AI Agents?

Chandra Khatri, Founding Head of AI @ Ola Krutrim

Moderator:
Savannah Kunovsky, Managing Director, Emerging Technology @ IDEO

Stage: io.net Main Stage
#superai #aiagents #chatbots #agenticai #ai

Recorded on 19 June 2025
